1
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:05,760
You're dreaming again.

2
00:02:15,159 --> 00:02:16,240
I will take responsibility

3
00:02:16,439 --> 00:02:17,919
for what happened yesterday.

4
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,039
Soon,

5
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:21,120
I will follow the customs of Qingyun State

6
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:21,960
and propose to your parents and brothers

7
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,000
with the betrothal gifts

8
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,000
to marry you properly.

9
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,479
What betrothal gifts do you have?

10
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:36,719
Well,

11
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,439
two pigs

12
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,439
and two cows.

13
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:45,159
According to the customs of Qingyun State,

14
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,960
I should have 50 taels of gold.

15
00:02:48,319 --> 00:02:49,199
But

16
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,560
I don't have much money

17
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:52,879
in your world.

18
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,520
So

19
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,759
I have to

20
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:57,840
owe you.

21
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:02,479
You got up early to write this?

22
00:03:03,159 --> 00:03:04,719
If you are not satisfied,

23
00:03:04,759 --> 00:03:06,639
you can follow the rules of your world.

24
00:03:07,439 --> 00:03:09,039
Do you know what happened last night?

25
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:12,479
I always act with integrity.

26
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:15,080
I'm not a heartless playboy.

27
00:03:15,599 --> 00:03:16,240
Last night...

28
00:03:16,439 --> 00:03:17,960
I kissed you when I was drunk.

29
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,000
I ruined your body.

30
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:20,319
I will take responsibility.

31
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:26,599
I, Yan Ying, will sing a song for everyone.

32
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:28,680
Gratitude.

33
00:03:28,759 --> 00:03:30,800
Thank you for being there.

34
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,599
Let me...

35
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:35,800
Let me have the courage to be myself.

36
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,360
It's your turn. Sing.

37
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:40,960
Ready.

38
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:41,879
Go.

39
00:03:42,439 --> 00:03:43,199
Sing.

40
00:03:43,199 --> 00:03:44,400
Are you going to sing or not?

41
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:46,560
If not, I'm off to bed.

42
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,960
You look strange.

43
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,319
What happened last night?

44
00:04:04,599 --> 00:04:05,400
Hmm.

45
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:10,360
Hmm.

46
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,279
You look...

47
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,000
So delicious.

48
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:28,560
I think I've been poisoned.

49
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,560
I need to sleep with you to cure it.

50
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,839
What happened last night?

51
00:04:54,959 --> 00:04:55,759
Nothing.

52
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,000
But you need to prepare more betrothal gifts.

53
00:04:58,199 --> 00:04:58,959
Otherwise, I won't agree.

54
00:05:00,079 --> 00:05:01,079
What do you mean?

55
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,199
Hey, you...

56
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:03,959
You were drunk last night.

57
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:05,240
I gave you a half-day off.

58
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,560
No need to go to work.

59
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:14,800
Chief Xu.

60
00:05:15,199 --> 00:05:15,439
Yes.

61
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:17,519
The board and the company have approved the acquisition plan.

62
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,439
You need to sign it.

63
00:05:18,959 --> 00:05:19,319
I see.

64
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:21,519
The people who are going to have a meeting are already in your office.

65
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,240
I didn't schedule a meeting today.

66
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,959
It's an important meeting.

67
00:05:26,439 --> 00:05:27,319
You'd better go to see them.

68
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:28,800
Okay.

69
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,600
I haven't seen you for so long.

70
00:05:45,079 --> 00:05:46,879
Don't you miss your beloved brother at all?

71
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,319
Didn't you say last night that you would welcome me back?

72
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,600
Why don't you wait for me?

73
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,879
I can only bring these gifts

74
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:55,800
to the office.

75
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,959
Xu Mengxi

76
00:05:58,399 --> 00:06:00,000
I have a lot of work to do.

77
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,399
I don't have time to play with you.

78
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:02,879
What a coincidence.

79
00:06:03,279 --> 00:06:05,279
I'm here to talk to you about work.

80
00:06:05,959 --> 00:06:06,959
A company overseas

81
00:06:07,079 --> 00:06:09,000
wants the VR game license of Galaxy Chronicle.

82
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,319
Think about it.

83
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:13,879
Galaxy Chronicle?

84
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,000
What does it have to do with me?

85
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,360
I'll give you time.

86
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,199
Think about it.

87
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:32,040
Belgian handmade chocolates.

88
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:34,040
Your favorite.

89
00:06:36,199 --> 00:06:36,639
Here.

90
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:37,680
Have a taste.

91
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,199
I'm not a child anymore.

92
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:45,360
Yes.

93
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:47,079
Okay.

94
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,360
Then let's

95
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,360
talk about adult matters.

96
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:54,120
During the time your brother was away,

97
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,920
did you have a relationship?

98
00:07:01,199 --> 00:07:01,920
Yes.

99
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,519
Your fans should see

100
00:07:06,519 --> 00:07:08,560
how you are.

101
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,399
I see.

102
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,720
You have a crush.

103
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:18,800
Hey.

104
00:07:19,199 --> 00:07:20,519
Don't tell my parents.

105
00:07:20,639 --> 00:07:22,519
It's a good thing.

106
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,480
At least it proves

107
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,759
you haven't been standing still.

108
00:07:27,079 --> 00:07:28,439
Don't pretend to be

109
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,600
a confidant who knows me well.

110
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:33,399
No one here needs your psychological counseling.

111
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,720
Let's make up.

112
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,759
We didn't argue.

113
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,319
Make up what?
